---
// Ebook Component - Sección promocional del E-book
---

<section class="py-24 bg-white" id="ebook">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-[3rem] p-8 lg:p-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 overflow-hidden relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-100 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                <img alt="Ebook Cover" class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-2xl rotate-2" src="/ebook/1.jpeg" />
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-8 relative">
                <div>
                    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-[var(--secondary)] text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Gratis por tiempo limitado</span>
                    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">10 Pasos para tu Proyecto Cultural</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Empieza hoy mismo con la metodología que he perfeccionado en más de 15 años de carrera.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/ebook" class="inline-block w-full text-center px-8 py-4 bg-[var(--primary)] text-white font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-purple-800 transition-all">
                    Quiero mi ebook
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
